textBeforeTable: Grass Homefield: Lambeau Field Green Bay Packers (8-4) Prediction: GB 27, CHI 20 Friday Night Update: Hester missed practice on Friday day as well. I am removing him from the projections now though he has not been ruled out. He has a bad matchup anyway and now is not healthy.
